data.loading-languages#Loading Languages:
Add the following to your fxmanifest to load all locales
files {
'bridge/**/**/client.lua',
'bridge/**/*.lua',
'locales/*.json'
}

data.installing-the-bridge#Installing The Bri:
For Developers Only
To be able to load the bridge you need to add the following to your fxmanifest.lua
lua54 'yes'
use_experimental_fxv2_oal 'yes'

shared_scripts {
'bridge/bridge.lua',
}

files {
'bridge/**/**/client.lua',
'bridge/**/*.lua',
}

